high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the fridge to the right of the stove.
Pick up a cup from the counter in front of the toaster.
Move to the sink in the middle of the counter to your left.
Place the cup in to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a golden cup in the sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter directly behind you, to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the wooden goblet from the counter.
Turn and go to the sink on your left.
Stand the goblet in the right front corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a wooden goblet in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup in the sink.
